      "acceptanceCriteria": "Version-controlled solver with regression test suite; documented release notes for CFD platform.",
      "rationale": "ANSYS Fluent 2022R2 used with institutional SQA protocol. Regression suite covers 98% of relevant solver modules. Achieved level meets required level for MRL 5 under Minimal profile review."
    },
    {
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Numerical code verification",
      "requiredLevel": 3,
      "achievedLevel": 3,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Method of manufactured solutions (MMS) applied to governing equations; order-of-accuracy confirmed.",
      "rationale": "MMS verification performed for incompressible Navier-Stokes with scalar transport. Second-order spatial accuracy confirmed. Achieved level meets required."
    },
    {
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Discretization error",
      "requiredLevel": 3,
      "achievedLevel": 3,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Grid convergence index (GCI) below 5% for hemolysis index QoI on three systematically refined meshes.",
      "rationale": "Three-mesh Richardson extrapolation yielded GCI of 3.8% for the primary hemolysis index quantity. Achieved level satisfies required level."
    },
    {
