      "acceptanceCriteria": "Experimental boundary conditions documented and traceable; flow rate and rotational speed match simulation inputs within 2%.",
      "rationale": "In-vitro test conditions recorded at 5 L/min, 2500 RPM. Boundary condition correspondence confirmed within 1.4%. Achieved level meets required."
