      "acceptanceCriteria": "Predicted hemolysis index within 15% of experimental mean; velocity field RMSE below 0.05 m/s.",
      "rationale": "Hemolysis index prediction deviated 11.2% from experimental mean. Velocity RMSE was 0.038 m/s. Both criteria satisfied."
    },
