      "acceptanceCriteria": "QoIs (hemolysis index, wall shear stress) directly linked to clinical endpoint of RBC damage.",
      "rationale": "Hemolysis index and peak shear stress are established surrogates for RBC lysis in the biofluid mechanics literature. QoI relevance confirmed."
