    "rationale": "Under the Minimal profile declaration, the seven assessed credibility factors all achieve their required levels, providing sufficient evidence to support an Accepted decision for the stated clinical research application. Six factors remain as documented epistemic gaps and are flagged for resolution prior to any regulatory submission. The absence of a structured Context of Use object is consistent with the Minimal profile; intended-use scope is conveyed narratively as application in clinical research for hemolysis risk characterization of centrifugal VAD pumps.",
